# Marshall CV506 â€“ Recording Guide

This document describes how to record video from the Marshall CV506 camera
using a computer and an HDMI capture card.

---

## Requirements

| Item | Description |
|-----|------------|
| Camera | Marshall CV506 |
| Output | HDMI |
| Capture | HDMI capture card (USB / PCIe) |
| OS | Windows / macOS / Linux |
| Software | FFmpeg |

---

## Install FFmpeg

### Windows
- Download: https://ffmpeg.org/download.html
- Add `ffmpeg.exe` to system PATH

Verify:
```powershell
ffmpeg -version
